# import tree
nwk <- read.newick("namecahnge.nwk")

namechanges <- read.delim("rename.txt", header=TRUE)
nwk_nc <- rename_taxa(nwk, namechanges, label, new)

# export basic, name-changed tree

Trees

The following trees were used to describe the population structure and visualise the pangenome analysis of Staphylococcus argenteus

Full species tree, population structure

This tree describes the MLST grouping (clonal complexes) of the species.

ggtree(nwk_nc) %<+% mlst +
      geom_tiplab(size=0.7) +
      geom_tippoint(aes(color=mlst), size=0.7) +
      scale_discrete_manual(values=hotnorth7, aesthetics = c("color")) +
      theme(legend.key.size=unit(3,"point")) +
      geom_cladelabel(node=412, label="ST1223", colour=hotnorth7[1], offset=0.0001) +
      geom_cladelabel(node=547, label="ST1850", colour=hotnorth7[2], offset=0.0001) +
      geom_cladelabel(node=459, label="ST2198", colour=hotnorth7[3], offset=0.0001) +
      geom_cladelabel(node=624, label="ST2250", colour=hotnorth7[4], offset=0.0001) +
      geom_cladelabel(node=396, label="ST2793", colour=hotnorth7[5], offset=0.0001) +
      geom_cladelabel(node=391, label="ST2854", colour=hotnorth7[6], offset=0.0001) +
      geom_cladelabel(node=543, label="ST4587", colour=hotnorth7[7], offset=0.0001)

Full species tree, with resistance mechanisms presented as a heatmap

This tree was used to examine patterns and inform further analysis.

pr <- ggtree(nwk_nc,  
            size=0.35) %<+% mlst +
      geom_tiplab(size=0.78) +
      geom_treescale(x=0.000125, y=350, fontsize=4, linesize=0.5, offset=2)
      #scale_discrete_manual(values=hotnorth7, aesthetics = c("color"))
      #geom_cladelabel(node=412, label="ST1223", offset=0.0002, align=TRUE) +
      #geom_cladelabel(node=547, label="ST1850", offset=0.0002, align=TRUE) +
      #geom_cladelabel(node=459, label="ST2198", offset=0.0002, align=TRUE) +
     # geom_cladelabel(node=624, label="ST2250", offset=0.0002, align=TRUE) +
      #geom_cladelabel(node=396, label="ST2793", offset=0.0002, align=TRUE) +
      #geom_cladelabel(node=391, label="ST2854", offset=0.0002, align=TRUE) +
      #geom_cladelabel(node=543, label="ST4587", offset=0.0002, align=TRUE)

resfinder <- as.data.frame(read.delim("resfinder.txt"))
tippies <- nwk_nc$tip.label
rownames(resfinder) <- tippies

MLST_HM <- as.data.frame(read.delim("mlst_heatmap.txt", header=FALSE))
rownames(MLST_HM) <- tippies

pr2 <- gheatmap(pr, MLST_HM, offset=0.00006, width=0.0175, colnames=FALSE, color="white") +
          scale_fill_manual(name= "Clonal Complex", values=hotnorth7, breaks=c("ST1223", "ST1850", "ST2198", "ST2250", "ST2793", "ST2854", "ST4587"))


pr3 <- pr2 + new_scale_fill()
  
pr3 <- gheatmap(pr3, resfinder, font.size=2, width=0.111, offset=0.000145, colnames_position = "top", color="white", colnames_angle=45, colnames_offset_y=3, colnames=FALSE) +
  scale_fill_manual(name="Resistance genes",
     breaks=c("blaZ", "mecA",
              "aph(3')-III", "ant(9)-Ia", "aac(6')-aph(2'')", "str",
              "tet(L)", "tet(K)",
              "erm(C)", "erm(A)",
              "qacA", "qacC",
              "dfrG",
              "cat",
              "fusB",
              "lnu(A)",
              "msr(A)",
              "vga(A)LC",
              "absent"), 
     values=c("#A72608", "#D6300A",
              "#3A7D44", "#479A53", "#57B265", "#73BF7F",
              "#24A899", "#46D8C7",
              "#016EB7", "#0186DF",
              "#FFA91F", "#FFC870",
              "#D6A2AD",
              "#595F72",
              "#C64191",
              "#CCE2A3",
              "#8338EC",
              "#122932",
              "white"))

pointfinder <- as.data.frame(read.delim("pointmu.txt"))
rownames(pointfinder) <- tippies

pr4 <- pr3 + new_scale_fill()

final <- gheatmap(pr4, pointfinder, colnames=FALSE, width=0.028, offset=0.0003925) +
  scale_fill_manual(name="Resistance mutations",
                    breaks=c("ileS", "grlA", "grlA + gyrA", "rpoB", "absent"),
                    values=c("#744077", "#1EAE70", "#74E7B5", "#454E9E", "white"))

Full species tree, SCCmec/CRISPR

This tree depicts the presence/absence and typing of SCCmec and CRISPR elements in the genomes of S argenteus

georegion <- read.delim("full_geog_region.txt", na="")
geoH <- as.data.frame(georegion$Region)
      rownames(geoH) <- georegion$tip.label
      colnames(geoH) <- "Region"
      
pscc <- ggtree(nwk_nc, layout="circular",  
            size=0.5) %<+% georegion +
      geom_tiplab(size=1, na.rm=TRUE)
      #geom_tippoint(aes(color=Region), size=1, alpha=0.75, na.rm=TRUE) +
      #scale_color_brewer("Region", palette="Set1", guide=guide_legend(order=1))

      #geom_treescale(x=0.000125, y=350, fontsize=4, linesize=0.5, offset=2)
      #scale_discrete_manual(values=hotnorth7, aesthetics = c("color"))
      #geom_cladelabel(node=412, label="ST1223", offset=0.0002, align=TRUE) +
      #geom_cladelabel(node=547, label="ST1850", offset=0.0002, align=TRUE) +
      #geom_cladelabel(node=459, label="ST2198", offset=0.0002, align=TRUE) +
     # geom_cladelabel(node=624, label="ST2250", offset=0.0002, align=TRUE) +
      #geom_cladelabel(node=396, label="ST2793", offset=0.0002, align=TRUE) +
      #geom_cladelabel(node=391, label="ST2854", offset=0.0002, align=TRUE) +
      #geom_cladelabel(node=543, label="ST4587", offset=0.0002, align=TRUE)

scc <- as.data.frame(read.delim("scc_crsp.txt"))
tippies <- nwk_nc$tip.label
rownames(scc) <- tippies

MLST_HM <- as.data.frame(read.delim("mlst_heatmap.txt", header=FALSE))
rownames(MLST_HM) <- tippies

pscc2 <- gheatmap(pscc, MLST_HM, offset=0.00025, width=0.03, colnames=FALSE, color="white") +
          scale_fill_manual(name= "Clonal Complex", guide=guide_legend(order=2),
                            values=hotnorth7, breaks=c("ST1223", "ST1850", "ST2198", "ST2250", "ST2793", "ST2854", "ST4587"))

pscc3 <- pscc2 + new_scale_fill()
  
pscc3 <- gheatmap(pscc3, scc, font.size=2, width=0.09, offset=0.000326, colnames_position = "top", color="white", colnames_angle=45, colnames_offset_y=3, colnames=FALSE) +
  scale_fill_manual(name="SCC composition", guide=guide_legend(order=3),
     breaks=c("CRISPR-Cas System",
              "Type IV", "Type IVa", "Type IVc", "dfrG", "Type IVd", "Type Vc", "mecA only",
              "absent"), 
     values=c("#380036",
              "#60E6C5", "#4F9ECF", "#11BB41", "#D6A2AD","#475A71", "#FFC857", "#D6300A",
              "white"))
pscc4 <- pscc3 + new_scale_fill()

pscc4 <- gheatmap(pscc4, geoH, width=0.03, colnames=FALSE, offset=0.000175, color="white") +
      scale_fill_brewer("Region", palette="Set1", guide=guide_legend(order=1)) +
      ggtitle(expression(paste("SCC", italic("mec"), " ", "Presence and Typing in", " ", italic("S. argenteus"))), "Species core SNP phylogeny produced by IQTree2")
